cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper deals with deep learning models and their calibration, which are topics that are commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on image classification and calibration, it is most likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) as these are the most relevant sub-fields for this topic.
